    "Description": "There's this small gang that continues to be a thorn in our side, and the bastards have just ambushed some friends over at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>. Seems like they're doing their best to destroy the <EM4>~mission(Objects)</EM4> there.\n\nI need you and whatever <EM4>crew you can muster</EM4> on site stopping these mungers from blowing everything up and protecting any <EM4>friendly ships</EM4> that need a hand.\n\nHandle this right and I\u2019ll give the main contractor  <EM4>~mission(ScripAmount) Council Scrip</EM4>.\n\n- Stows",
